                        Calculation of the Standardised
                        Precipitation-Evapotranspiration Index
SPEINews                Show the NEWS file
kern                    Time kernel for computing the SPEI at different
                        time scales.
pglo                    Generalized Logistic distribution function.
print.spei              Generic methods for 'spei' objects.
spei                    Calculation of the Standardized
                        Precipitation-Evapotranspiration Index (SPEI)
                        and the Standardized Precipitation Index (SPI).
thornthwaite            Computation of potential evapotranspiration.
wichita                 Datasets for illustrating the functions in the
                        SPEI package.
